kuttyedathi ( malayalam : കുട ട യേടത തി , english : kutty , the elder sister ) is a 1971 malayalam language film directed by p. n. menon and written by m. t. vasudevan nair . widely regarded as one of the best south indian films made in the 1970s . the other cast and crew - music m.s.baburaj , cinematography ashok kumar , operative cameraman p. s. nivas and editing ravi kiran . kuttyedathi is woven around the life of a girl , who is an ugly duckling with tomboyish tendencies , and who is continuously discriminated against in favour of her prettier younger sister.location of this film is shoranur